column8: planet_threshold_desc:I didn't take everything. I took the higher digs and moved on. I didn't want to take all the gems.
column10: dig_threshold_desc:I left after getting the higher counts. I didn't stick around and take everything.
column12: surprise_desc:If it dropped from 100 to say 40 I would leave the planet.
column14: dynamic_desc:Some yielded higher digs for a long time so I stayed until there was a sharp drop in gem counts.
column16: other_desc:I just collected the most gems Up front and left when they dropped really low.
